{"tid":1611232,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"新職業-遠攻（可討論）","createTime":"2019-10-02T01:56:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T12:40:39.000Z","uid":150705,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"c98eadefcbf9a76fe4b572015f17089ac0422cb7","tid":1611232,"uid":150705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:56:56.000Z","msg":"琴日經歷沙田一役，我哋喺好運商場上嘅制高點，而狗就喺下面源禾路，我哋有護牆嘅優勢，所以佢地射唔到我哋。有好多師兄係咁用手使用土，水，火魔法，問題係狗距離我哋50米，完全dum唔中。而旁邊有師兄用decathlon阻力帶射嘢過去，係中撚哂。我哋應該研究點樣改良呢啲阻力帶，令佢兼備火水土魔法。<br />\n<br />\n土：唔使改良都發射到<br />\n<br />\n水：發射一刻衝力太大，個波會爆，可能要加個發射底盤<br />\n<br />\n火：未試過，希望有人提供意見<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n既然我哋同狗嘅距離越嚟越遠，遠攻就係唯一出路"},{"pid":"5ebf6ab31424ca5f81477ef5cba424ddf008db2d","tid":1611232,"uid":108337,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:02:17.000Z","msg":"大量買阻力帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b6b7667496fb55e22cf31a248fcb8b1864b688a","tid":1611232,"uid":160842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:04:23.000Z","msg":"今日12點半，黑西裝癱瘓全中環！！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1610862\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1610862</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KXztoQ5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKXztoQ5.jpg&h=00d883ed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3aWjvv5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3aWjvv5.jpg&h=1e37b9ca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oBbLq4r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoBbLq4r.jpg&h=ce3e3bcd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"909537f1328c148010899af8e24f9c96cfc10f3d","tid":1611232,"uid":150705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:25:19.000Z","msg":"阻力帶！"},{"pid":"600a9012d9ee2abde7bca3d57ba9bb891ee9ef33","tid":1611232,"uid":158889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10