l/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:24:18.000Z","msg":"可以，揾個大盆裝水，mix哂全部材料，再分裝入吱吱樽，吱落氣球到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nmix嘢（1人，要熟份量）<br />\n幫氣球打氣（2-3人）<br />\n吱嘢入氣球（5人）<br />\n旁觀嘅人就幫手收集材料同斟水！"},{"pid":"f3a4e5194dba865dd20a10b0e4aa4dc7e330d3f0","tid":1611232,"uid":288179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f11b63ef9d2a137ab14c03d43e217dbf7ea9076d","tid":1611232,"uid":150705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41a467ba049e233e5885feba67f098f68f5aa1a9","tid":1611232,"uid":288179,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:05:42.000Z","msg":"發射器材料：<br />\n迪卡儂15kg 拉力帶兩條<br />\n五金鋪漏斗一個<br />\n3M保溫膠紙一卷<br />\n<br />\n制作工具：<br />\n剪鉗<br />\n細十字螺絲批<br />\n沙紙<br />\n<br />\n經過發夢驗試，暫時可以穩定射出罐裝野飲。漆彈就有機會射出去個陣自爆，主要睇漆彈整成點。因為發夢個陣射左太耐，個發射器都有損壞左。聽日會買材料，整個步驟出黎，希望大家可以大量生產，唔洗次次發惡夢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:17:58.000Z","msg":"保温膠紙係for緩衝？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:26:17.000Z","msg":"係 我地經試左好多次 因為個漏斗係硬 當拉行拉力帶放手個下 加速得太快 如果係漆彈就一定會爆 加左保溫膠紙就大大減低左自爆既機會"},{"pid":"5dad226be70895e91f9c8c80af0f25ff6c4b2dac","tid":1611232,"uid":143210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48a45478ff0cf35567e3bfb00e1b08b931b9da9e","tid":1611232,"uid":150705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34642d8d1351ca9679e523baa61735450ebe06d0","tid":1611232,"uid":143210,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:42:44.000Z","msg":"火嘅樽底向目標"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:46:50.000Z","msg":"個樽身會唔會好啲？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:26:20.000Z","msg":"旋轉快啲咁，會唔會風火輪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bcae599537555a1fd3bfa4010bb45e448d9d591","tid":1611232,"uid":294787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73fedd7156686c44f2407d1c73d6d94ffa0e62e2","tid":1611232,"uid":6845,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:43:33.000Z",